        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "**3. 天然气**"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "天然气的主要成分是**甲烷（CH₄）**。"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "甲烷燃烧："
        },
        {
          "type": "equation",
          "latex": "CH_4 + 2O_2 \\xrightarrow{点燃} CO_2 + 2H_2O",
          "display": true
